    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test Conditions factor below required level (achieved 2, required 3). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. The Test Conditions gap is offset by the strong quantitative agreement across all three QoIs (maximum E/uval = 1.42, all within 10% percent difference) and the inter-laboratory consistency of bench test results. The model risk level 3 assessment is supported by medium model influence and medium decision consequence. Regulatory submission may proceed with explicit documentation of the single test condition limitation.",
